French director Luc Besson has announced that Chinese-Canadian actor Kris Wu will join his latest science fiction film 'Valerian'.
Being a former member of EXO and the former leader of its sub-group, EXO-M, Kris Wu has recently been most active in China. The 25-year-old pop idol has starred in several hit Chinese movies including 'Mr. Six' and 'L.O.R.D.: Legend of Ravaging Dynasties'.
